# TradingFlow Core Rules

- Use Bun commands for workspace tasks (`bun run`, `bun add`, `bun test`).
- Preserve existing user changes; do not revert unrelated edits.
- Report whether an issue is newly introduced or pre-existing.
- Run targeted lint/type checks after substantive edits.
- Keep route names and API paths consistent across client and backend.
